comments: Harden (HOU) makes some contact with Kleber (DAL) during the rebound but does not affect his ability to retrieve the ball.
Paul (HOU) places a hand/arm to the front of Hardaway Jr. (DAL) at the start of the drive but the contact does not affect his SQBR.
RLB shows Harden (HOU) cleanly blocks Hardaway Jr.'s (DAL) driving shot attempt.
LAR shows Finney-Smith (DAL) moves laterally into Paul's (HOU) path during the pick and contact affect his SQBR.
Tucker (HOU) cleanly dislodges the pass attempt to Doncic (DAL). Any ensuing contact is considered incidental.
Tucker (HOU)  slightly extends his arm against Powell (DAL) as he is going for the loose ball but the contact is marginal.
Hardaway Jr. (DAL) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Paul (HOU) and gives him room to avoid contact.
Harden (HOU) establishes himself in a legal position in the path of Brunson (DAL) and firms up on his shoulder but he is able to move through the contact.
[Observable in enhanced video] Harden (HOU) slides his pivot foot at the start of his dribble.
Harden (HOU) makes contact with Brunson (DAL) off ball but does not affect his ability to defend the pass.
Brunson (DAL) makes contact to the body of Harden (HOU) after the release that does not affect his jump shot attempt.
Doncic (DAL) makes some contact with Tucker (HOU) during the rebound but does not affect his ability to retrieve the ball.
Finney-Smith (DAL) establishes himself in a legal position in the path of Tucker (HOU) and gives him room to avoid contact.
Harden (HOU) takes a step forward into Doncic's (DAL) body but he is able to continue through the contact on his path to the basket.
Capela (HOU) is in the paint for less than three seconds when he is imminently actively guarding an opponent.
Capela (HOU) makes marginal contact to the arm of Powell (DAL) during his shooting motion that does not affect his play at the basket.
[Observable in enhanced video] Harden (HOU) lifts his pivot foot at the start of his dribble.
Brunson (DAL) places a hand/arm to the front of Harden (HOU) during the drive but the contact does not affect his SQBR.
Powell (DAL) makes marginal contact to Harden's (HOU) body during his shooting motion that does not affect his driving shot attempt.
Powell (DAL) establishes himself in a legal position in the path of Tucker (HOU) and makes marginal contact that does not prevent him from disengaging from the play.
RLB shows Paul (HOU) cleanly blocks Brunson's (DAL) shot attempt.
